caption.text: This is 'sarubobo' さるぼぼ (a baby monkey) It is a Japanese amulet from Takayama the differently colors sarubobos are each associated with different wishes;   sarubobo - for luck in study and work  sarubobo - for luck in love  sarubobo - for luck in health  sarubobo - for luck in money  sarubobo - to remove bad luck There is also a differently-shaped sarubobo called a "tobibobo."
